{"tid":999931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美醫院認錯同名同姓同齡腦死病人 拿錯授權拔喉","createTime":"2019-01-29T05:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T11:19:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf89b6ebc0175848e2173e03b8989b8221f8684","tid":999931,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:44:51.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）紐約發生罕見醫療行政失當事故，一間醫院去年懷疑因人為疏忽，誤認一名腦死病人是另一名同名同姓同齡的男子，並通知錯家屬。該病人最終在陌生人同意下，拔除生命維持儀器離世。<br />\n事發於去年7月15日。40歲男子威廉斯（Freddy Clarence Williams）在家中濫藥後，失去知覺，被送往布朗克斯（The Bronx）的聖巴拿巴醫院（St. Barnabas Hospital）。當時他身上有身份證明文件，但院方只核對其姓名和年齡，未有確認社會保障號碼，因此把他誤認是第二位同名同姓同齡男子威廉斯（Freddy Williams），並錯誤通知其家屬。<br />\n第二名威廉斯的48歲姊姊鮑威爾（Shirell Powell）接報後抵達醫院，由於床上的威廉斯口部插了喉，戴了頸箍，眼皮、鼻子、面部浮腫，讓鮑威爾難以確認其面貌，甚至覺得他與自己的弟弟相似，因此一直未有質疑院方的講法。<br />\n病人留院兩日後，院方證實他腦幹死亡，不可能恢復意識，一度令鮑威爾哭得死去活來。後來鮑威爾接受現實，安排親友逐一來見「弟弟」最後一面，其間鮑威爾另一名姊妹曾指出，床上的威廉斯身形較胖，不像其弟弟，但鮑威爾指出病人全身浮腫，才令她有「較胖」的錯覺。<br />\n到7月29日，鮑威爾在病人昏迷14日後，同意院方拔除生命維持儀器。院方在安排解剖驗屍時，才發現死者並非鮑威爾的弟弟。鮑威爾後來才發現，弟弟同月1日因干犯襲擊罪而被捕，一直被羈留，並失去聯絡。<br />\n當鮑威爾得悉自己的弟弟仍在生，自己卻在醫院誤導下，了結一名陌生人的生命，一度令她暈倒，之後不時失眠。她曾要求院方提供死者的個人資料，讓她向其家屬致哀並解釋，但被院方以私隱為由拒絕。<br />\n到近日她決定入稟控告院方失誤，要求賠償，事件才曝光。院方發言人回應稱，有關索償沒有任何理據支持，並對事件沒有補充。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190128/large/1548688296_da0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190128%2Flarge%2F1548688296_da0c.jpg&h=abcde2eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鮑威爾被聖巴拿巴醫院誤導，誤認陌生腦死病人是自己的弟弟，而授權院方終止其生命。"},{"pid":"87cf292c96c171c797ce35ff13e211faea4f85d7","tid":999931,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:46:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fc478b17298506491c5f91088cc898db4ee4215","tid":999931,"uid":48408,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:47:59.000Z","msg":"單野都幾多巧合 注定條友都<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116ff72cb4621d018658cacc1c4918dafd89d46e","tid":999931,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鮑威爾後來才發現，弟弟同月1日因干犯襲擊罪而被捕，一直被羈留，並失去聯絡。</blockquote><br />\n咁橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609206d56bddfdd00f1463e66a8f64a9cddafca1","tid":999931,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7fc478b17298506491c5f91088cc898db4ee4215","tid":999931,"uid":48408,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:47:59.000Z","msg":"單野都幾多巧合 注定條友都<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:57:10.000Z","msg":"本身條友已經腦死"},{"pid":"03dc4074ab856c6f07530e335dc32cf3d74706a6","tid":999931,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:01:25.000Z","msg":"腦死<br />\n俾著真屋企人都係做一樣決定<br />\n<br />\n但係做落決定果個就無黎啦肺好似有責任咁<br />\n<br />\n白人可能會內疚<br />\n但係黑人啦喎多數想r賠償咋"},{"pid":"ad80d23e168c14f860f737443fdbd6e70939d160","tid":999931,"uid":189528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"同名同姓一個黑一個白會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c2609162c3e30f9b9e14557a95435531021944","tid":999931,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:37:41.000Z","msg":"連自己友都分唔到黑人邊個打邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de877a8400f208523b83c4d4ce1f048e7a71c442","tid":999931,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad80d23e168c14f860f737443fdbd6e70939d160","tid":999931,"uid":189528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"同名同姓一個黑一個白會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:51:47.000Z","msg":"咁一定分得出啦"},{"pid":"f9239e23a0bff473f8d4519e15ca008294c5d260","tid":999931,"uid":112606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:45:07.000Z","msg":"仲以為係2個人訓同一間醫院搞錯，<br />\n原來另一個根本唔係醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944c79311a414d0847c8fb1e8645caa470741213","tid":999931,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9239e23a0bff473f8d4519e15ca008294c5d260","tid":999931,"uid":112606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:45:07.000Z","msg":"仲以為係2個人訓同一間醫院搞錯，<br />\n原來另一個根本唔係醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:15:39.000Z","msg":"Me too<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36992523f722fb96d99485466f9e6ba3ec52b4a8","tid":999931,"uid":26601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:19:33.000Z","msg":"黑人既缺憾<br />\n個個望落都一樣，連自己親人都認唔到，無得唔認啦掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}